Access Modifiers:
1) private
    We can't access private members from other classes.
    - Fields    - static, non-static fields
    - Methods
    - Constructors
    - Class can't be private.

2) package-private:
    - default access modifier
    - package level access

3) public
    - Visible to all classes from other packages too.

